{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "阿尔贝里亚骑士道 希望与绝望",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "利弗和赛希尔越狱后与白燕骑士团的\\n侦察兵一同打算与同伴会合。\\n即将逃离格拉姆斯之际，利弗邀请\\n赛希尔成为伙伴。正当赛希尔犹豫时，\\n哈尔再次现身并揭露了赛希尔的过去。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "利弗和赛希尔\\n虽成功越狱，但……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "利～弗！\\n你不吃魔养石吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔，你冷静点……呜嗯！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "来来来～吃吧！\\n你可是白燕骑士团的团长大人，\\n得更强壮一点才行！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "咔咔咔……啊呜啊呜……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "呼！\\n魔养石，太～好吃了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "（刚一越狱就跑去买魔养石，\\n然后就开始暴饮暴食……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "（虽然她说啃一啃\\n能让心情平静下来，\\n但这不就是耍酒疯吗……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "利弗？\\n你怎么没动嘴啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "啊，嗯……我正要吃。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "咔咔咔……啊呜啊呜……\\n……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "怎么样？\\n感觉身体轻了很多吧？\\n整个人状态也变好了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "感觉这才叫……调养生息……\\n啊……太棒了！\\n魔养石，万岁！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "（说实话，我感觉没变化……\\n为什么她能醉成这样……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "几分钟后——",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "呜呜……简直想死。\\n不，让我去死。\\n我竟然对你那样发疯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "别、别在意……\\n你忍了这么久没碰魔养石，\\n也是难免的……吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "不过，你冷静下来就好。\\n逃离格拉姆斯的计划\\n我们再……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "团长！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "你是……弗雷德！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "他是谁啊？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "是我团里的部下。\\n你怎么会在这里？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗雷德",
            "context": "我们被迫和团长分开后，\\n分成了回新阿尔贝里亚\\n和营救团长的两组人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗雷德",
            "context": "得知您被困在\\n格拉姆斯教会后，\\n我就作为侦察兵潜了进去。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "是这样啊，\\n让你们费心了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗雷德",
            "context": "请往这边走。\\n其它营救小队准备了一条\\n从东面森林穿出去的脱身路线。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "好。\\n赛希尔，我们走。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "嗯、嗯……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗雷德",
            "context": "穿过这片森林就是边境了，\\n有营救小队在那边等候。\\n请在被追兵发现之前尽快动身。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "利弗……我真的可以\\n继续这样跟着你吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "当然，留在格拉姆斯的话\\n你就危险了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "但是……我已经不是骑士了。\\n你的部下没有义务救我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "你之前救过我，\\n就当是我报恩吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "是吗……\\n那好吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔……你果然还是\\n不想来新阿尔贝里亚吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "我依然希望\\n你能成为我们的伙伴。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "唔……我都说了不行吧？\\n我已经无法当回骑士……\\n没有资格再为王室而战了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "那从头再来就好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "从头再来？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "你至今都在后悔没能救下\\n亚罗拉斯王……对吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "但那不是你一个人的责任，\\n是阿尔贝里亚所有骑士的失职。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "正因如此，所有人\\n都平等拥有前进的机会。\\n你当然也不例外。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "赛希尔，如果你有\\n重新成为骑士的意愿……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "要不要试着再次侍奉明君，\\n为国与民而战呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "不管出于什么理由，你不顾危险\\n救了被人追捕的我是事实。\\n你的本性还是和从前一样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "我相信这样的你，\\n一定能重新踏上\\n曾畅谈不尽的骑士道。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "啊……啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "塞、赛希尔！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "哈！抱歉……\\n我差点就要消失了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "你对我说那种荣耀的理想\\n实在太耀眼……我都快融化了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "耀眼？\\n我没看到有什么光啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "我……我是指你说的话啦！\\n对于受挫的人来说简直是毒药……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "抱、抱歉！\\n我没打算伤害你……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "你这个人一本正经的……\\n事到如今还要\\n再给我补上一刀……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "我也没办法啊！\\n毕竟这就是我的真实想法……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "真的吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "你真的认为我这么\\n落魄的人还能从头再来？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "当然。所以赛希尔，\\n跟我一起走吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（其实我……很想握住这只手。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（我一直都知道……不能继续\\n自甘堕落。但是，想重拾过去\\n却总是无法付诸行动。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（也许现在正是重来的机会。\\n但是……我不知道\\n是否有资格握住这只手。）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "（因为我……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "你跟他去也无妨哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "只不过，到时候\\n这群人就没命了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "老板娘",
            "context": "塞、赛希尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "佣兵",
            "context": "抱歉……是我疏忽了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "各位！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "对了，不止是他们哦。\\n反正佣兵的命就是随用随丢的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "就算那个公会不幸遭遇火灾，\\n对格拉姆斯来说\\n也不疼不痒哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "哈尔！\\n你怎么这般残忍……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "哎呀，对赛希尔来说，\\n这个选择应该不难做才对啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "你说什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "利弗……难道你还不知道\\n她以前干的好事？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "赛希尔",
            "context": "哈尔！求求你……不要……\\n不要说……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22902_04_0078",
            "book_image": ""
